we're gonna examine pantheons:

193
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:24,820
the groups of gods that feature in stories from different cultures, and how they function in those cultures.

194
00:11:24,820 --> 00:11:27,780
And then we're gonna take a look at how the universe was destroyed--

195
00:11:27,780 --> 00:11:30,440
looking at flood myths and the apocalypse.

196
00:11:30,440 --> 00:11:33,280
Now, obviously this puts us in the realm of religion

